l bring in the \\\"SOUL\\\" persona to make it genuine and proactive. Alright, let’s get that pleasant response ready!\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey there! I’m online and ready. How can I help you today? Do you want a quick check-in on tasks, a status update, or to dive into something AI-assisted right now?\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"openrouter/auto\",\"usage\":{\"input\":5098,\"output\":189,\"cacheRead\":3328,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":8615,\"cost\":{\"input\":-5098,\"output\":-189,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":-5287}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773207698452}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"161310b9\",\"parentId\":\"46268b23\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:44:13.411Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 05:44 UTC] hello\"}],\"timestamp\":1773207853405}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"44fd3547\",\"parentId\":\"161310b9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:44:17.540Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Greeting the user**\\n\\nI'm thinking we should greet the user concisely and ask what they need. I want to offer them some quick actions without recalling any past interactions. My reply could be: \\\"Hey! Good to see you. What would you like to do? You can check status, see your schedule, check memory, or run a task.\\\" I should keep the tone engaging and friendly, and no tools are necessary just yet!\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey hey! Great to hear from you. What would you like to do today? Here are a few quick options:\\n\\n- Quick status: summarize what I’m tracking for you right now\\n- Check memory: pull up recent notes or memory snippets\\n- Schedule a reminder or cron task\\n- Run a quick test or fetch some info (weather, status, etc.)\\n- Start a deeper AI-assisted task (draft, analysis, coding, etc.)\\n\\nTell me what you want, or just say “hi” and I’ll guide you.\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"openrouter/auto\",\"usage\":{\"input\":229,\"output\":247,\"cacheRead\":8320,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":8796,\"cost\":{\"input\":-229,\"output\":-247,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":-476}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773207853408}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"6d7256b5\",\"parentId\":\"44fd3547\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T07:08:22.803Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 07:08 UTC] 你好\"}],\"timestamp\":1773212902788}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e82db1a1\",\"parentId\":\"6d7256b5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T07:08:23.248Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"openrouter/auto\",\"usage\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":0,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"error\",\"timestamp\":1773212902795,\"errorMessage\":\"403 Key limit exceeded (total limit). Manage it using https://openrouter.ai/settings/keys\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"28fdf8c3\",\"parentId\":\"e82db1a1\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T08:56:15.087Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 08:56 UTC] 你