{"type":"message","id":"0c0426b6","parentId":"21ea82d3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:06:33.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has asked me to read the session file content directly in the message. I've just read it. Now I need to present it clearly in my response. The file is a JSONL file with multiple lines, each being a JSON object representing events in the session (message, tool calls, etc.).\n\nI'll format it as a code block to show the raw content. The user specifically said \"直接在消息里回复我该文件内容\" which means \"reply with the file content directly in the message.\"\n\nI should output the content as-is, likely in a code block for readability, but since they want it directly, I could just paste it. However, the file is quite long. I'll provide it as a code block with the JSON content. I'll keep the response concise and just show the file.\n\nLet me present it nicely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"以下是会话记录的完整内容（JSONL 格式）:\n\n```json\n{\"type\":\"session\",\"version\":3,\"id\":\"a930fc8d-a281-43b3-979c-0f9520754365\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:38.419Z\",\"cwd\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"}\n{\"type\":\"model_change\",\"id\":\"5cd7a016\",\"parentId\":null,\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:38.428Z\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"modelId\":\"openrouter/auto\"}\n{\"type\":\"thinking_level_change\",\"id\":\"f26a86ff\",\"parentId\":\"5cd7a016\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:38.429Z\",\"thinkingLevel\":\"low\"}\n{\"type\":\"custom\",\"customType\":\"model-snapshot\",\"data\":{\"timestamp\":1773207698437,\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"modelApi\":\"openai-completions\",\"modelId\":\"openrouter/auto\"},\"id\":\"8f9a3fcf\",\"parentId\":\"f26a86ff\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:38.437Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"396eeb6f\",\"parentId\":\"8f9a3fcf\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:38.461Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 05:41 UTC] Wake up, my friend!\"}],\"timestamp\":1773207698445}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"46268b23\",\"parentId\":\"396eeb6f\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:41:41.973Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Crafting a friendly response**\\n\\nI want to start with a warm greeting and ask what the user has planned for today. Since it's a wake message, I need to follow the guidelines and keep it friendly. There's no need to mention tool use or memory steps; I'll keep my response concise. Additionally, I'll bring in the \\\"SOUL\\\" persona to make it genuine and proactive. Alright, let's get that pleasant response ready!\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey there! I'm online and ready. How can I help you today? Do you want a quick check-in on tasks, a status update, or to dive into something AI-assisted right now?\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"openrouter/auto\",\"usage\":{\"input\":5098,\"output\":189,\"cacheRead\":3328,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":8615,\"cost\":{\"input\":-5098,\"output\":-189,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":-5287}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773207698452}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"161310b9\",\"parentId\":\"46268b23\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:44:13.411Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 05:44 UTC] hello\"}],\"timestamp\":1773207853405}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"44fd3547\",\"parentId\":\"161310b9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T05:44:17.540Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Greeting the user**\\n\\nI'm thinking we should greet the user concisely and ask what they need. I want to offer them some quick actions without recalling any past interactions. My reply could be: \\\"Hey! Good to see you. What would you like to do? You can check status, see your schedule, check memory, or run a task.\\\" I should keep the tone engaging and friendly, and no tools are necessary just yet!\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey hey! Great to hear from you. What would you like to do today? Here are a few quick options:\\n\\n- Quick status: summarize what I'm tracking for you right now\\n- Check memory: pull up recent notes or memory snippets\\n- Schedule a reminder or cron task\\n- Run a quick test or fetch some info (weather, status, etc.)\\n- Start a deeper AI-assisted task (draft, analysis, coding, etc.)\\n\\nTell me what you want, or just say \\\"hi\\\" and I'll guide you.\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"openrouter/auto\",\"usage\":{\"input\":229,\"output\":247,\"cacheRead\":8320,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":8796,\"cost\":{\"input\":-229,\"output\":-247,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":-476}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773207853408}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"6d7256b5\",\"parentId\":\"44fd3547\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T07:08:22.803Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 07:08 UTC] \\u4f60\\u597d\"}],\"timestamp\":1773212902788}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e82db1a1\",\"parentId\":\"6d7256b5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T07:08:23.248Z\",\"message\":{\"role\"