**：检测到 2 个危险配置标志启用\\n- ⚠️ **警告**：部分节点命令拒绝规则不生效\\n\\n建议尽快修复安全配置，尤其是关闭 Control UI 的危险标志，除非是临时调试场景。\\n\\n需要我帮你进一步检查详细配置或进行安全修复吗？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":12950,\"output\":819,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":13769,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773229844467}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"9cf6dc72\",\"parentId\":\"c8bab993\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T11:51:33.466Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 11:51 UTC] 如果启动 Control UI 的设备身份验证，会有什么影响\"}],\"timestamp\":1773229893462}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e08cd82b\",\"parentId\":\"9cf6dc72\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T11:51:39.392Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is asking about the impact of enabling Control UI device authentication. This is related to the security warning we saw in the status output. I should provide a clear, concise explanation in Chinese about what happens when device identity checks are enabled for the Control UI.\\n\\nBased on the knowledge from the status output:\\n- Currently `gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth=true` is set, which disables device identity checks.\\n- The warning says: \\\"Control UI device auth disabled\\\"\\n\\nI need to explain:\\n1. What device authentication does\\n2. Why it's important for security\\n3. What impact it has on usage\\n4. Best practices\\n\\nI don't need to use any tools for this - it's a conceptual question about the OpenClaw system. I should explain it clearly in Chinese.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"启用 Control UI 的设备身份验证会带来以下影响：\\n\\n## 安全性提升\\n- ✅ 只有经过认证的设备（通过设备密钥或 TLS 客户端证书）才能访问 Control UI\\n- ✅ 防止未授权的本地/网络访问，即使有人知道 URL 也无法直接登录\\n- ✅ 减少攻击面，避免恶意脚本或中间人攻击\\n\\n## 使用的变化\\n- ⚠️ 首次访问 Control UI 时需要通过 `openclaw control-ui auth` 或类似流程进行设备配对\\n- ⚠️ 如果通过反向代理或远程访问，需要确保代理传递设备身份信息\\n- ✅ 本地 localhost 访问通常不受影响（默认信任本地设备）\\n\\n## 配置影响\\n- 需要将 `gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth` 设为 `false`（或删除该配置）\\n- 可能需要设置 `gateway.trustedProxies`（如果使用反向代理）\\n- 如果开启了 `gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth`，建议同时关闭，除非有特殊调试需求\\n\\n## 总结\\n启用后安全性显著提高，但对访问流程增加了一步验证。对于生产环境或任何暴露在外的部署，**强烈建议启用设备身份验证**。\\n\\n要我帮你立即开启设备身份验证并验证配置吗？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":13091,\"output\":648,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":13739,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773229893464}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"1a9c72ac\",\"parentId\":\"e08cd82b\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T11:52:39.620Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Wed 2026-03-11 11:52 UTC] \\u597d\\u7684\\uff0c\\u542f\\u7528 Control UI \\u7684\\u8bbe\\u5907\\u8eab\\u4efd\\u9a8c\\u8bc1\"}],\"timestamp\":1773229959617}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"73e93db1\",\"parentId\":\"1a9c72ac\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T11:52:46.791Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户希望启用 Control UI 的设备身份验证。从之前的 status 输出中，我们看到危险配置：\\n- gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth=true 是严重问题\\n- gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true 是警告\\n\\n需要编辑 OpenClaw 的配置文件来关闭这些危险设置。\\n\\n我需要找到配置文件。通常 OpenClaw 的配置可能在：\\n- ~/.openclaw/config.yaml (或 ~/.openclaw/config.yml)\\n- /etc/openclaw/config.yaml\\n- 用户目录下的配置\\n\\n让我先检查常见的配置位置。由于这是一个 gateway 配置，可能在 ~/.openclaw/ 或 /etc/openclaw/。\\n\\n让我先检查 ~/.openclaw/ 目录结构。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_7f06769b7e4343edbbe327f9\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"ls -la ~/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"No ~/.openclaw directory\\\"\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free\",\"usage\":{\"input\":13438,\"output\":408,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":13846,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773229959619}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"acae548f\",\"parentId\":\"73e93db1\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T11:52:56.182Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_7f06769b7e4343edbbe327f9\",\"toolName\":\"exec\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\u603b\\u8ba1 76\\ndrwx------ 11 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 11:42 .\\ndrwx------ 10 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 11:49 ..\\ndrwx------  3 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 03:15 agents\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 05:41 canvas\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 06:06 completions\\ndrwx------  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 05:41 cron\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 50 devices\\n-rw-------  1 root root  171  3\\u6708 11 08:59 exec-approvals.json\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 05:41 identity\\ndrwx------  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 03:48 logs\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096  3\\u6708 11 42 memory\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2414  3\\u6708 11 40 openclaw.json\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2512  3\\u6708 11 40 openclaw.json.bak\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2512  3\\u6708 11 34 openclaw.json.bak.1\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2512  3\\u6708 11 33 openclaw.json.bak.2\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2489  3\\u6708 11 29 openclaw.json.bak.3\\n-rw-------  1 root root 2371  3\\u6708 11 25 openclaw.json.bak.4\\n-rw-------  1 root root   49  3\\u6708 11 05:41 update-check.json\\ndrwxr-xr-x  4 roo